         <p>
          Jeri Muoio was first elected Mayor of the City of West Palm Beach March 2011. She was reelected to the office of Mayor in March 2015.  She previously served on the West Palm Beach City Commission for four years, having been reelected twice by the voters.

      <div class="section color--steelBlue" id="section-explore">
       <h3 class="section__title section__title--bg-white align--center toUpperCase color--blue">
        <span class="section__sub-title">
         LIVE. WORK. PLAY.
        </span>
        in paradise
       </h3>
       <div class="wpb--container--890">
        <div class="align--center" id="explorer__content">
         <div class="explorer__content__slider">
          <div class="explorer__content__box">
           <div class="explorer__content__box__img">
            <img alt="City" src="/CMSPages/GetAmazonFile.aspx?path=~\wpb_website\media\wpb_content\wpb_01_south_waterfront_pb_crop_pano.jpg&amp;hash=fb966d125b39ef1954f2872fa0f99852dc6da39068fc92b935f44619d95e0a26"/>
           </div>
           <p>
            <strong>
             You’ll love living here
            </strong>
